B.a0w=new A.m(B.bD,["Blessed is He in whose hand is dominion, and He is over all things competent. He who created death and life to test you as to which of you is best in deed - and He is the Exalted in Might, the Forgiving.","M\xfclk elinde olan ne y\xfccedir! O her \u015feye kadirdir. Hanginizin daha g\xfczel amel yapaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 denemek i\xe7in \xf6l\xfcm\xfc ve hayat\u0131 yaratan O'dur. O, Az\xeez'dir, Gaf\xfbr'dur."],t.w)
